Description: Comprehensive system control center for Guide OS
 Primo Di Tutto is an all-in-one system management and configuration tool
 that brings powerful administration features to your fingertips.
 .
 Key Features:
  * System Information: Hardware detection (CPU, GPU, RAM), kernel info
  * Device Management: USB and PCI device monitoring with detailed information
  * Software Management: Install/remove packages, manage repositories
  * Desktop Customization: Pre-configured layouts, themes, icons, cursors
  * System Tools: Process monitor, log viewer, service management
  * Network Configuration: Connection settings and diagnostics
  * User Management: Account administration and permissions
  * Layout Backup: Save and restore your desktop configurations
 .
 Inspired by openSUSE's YaST but designed with the user-friendliness and
 elegance of Linux Mint, Primo Di Tutto makes system administration
 accessible to both beginners and advanced users.